<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Credit Jambo</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            margin: -20px -20px 30px -20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 20px 20px 20px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .welcome-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        .account-details {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .account-details .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .account-details .row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .account-details .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }
        .account-details .value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Credit Jambo!</h1>
            <p>Your Digital Credit & Savings Partner</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

            <div class="welcome-box">
                <p style="margin-top: 0;">ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations! Your Credit Jambo account has been successfully created.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">We're excited to help you achieve your financial goals with our digital credit and savings platform.</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Your Account Details</h3>
            <div class="account-details">
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Customer ID:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{customerId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Email:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{email}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Initial Credit Score:</span>
                    <span class="value highlight">300 points</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>What's Next?</h3>
            <p>We've automatically set up your accounts:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Savings Account</strong> - Start saving with competitive interest rates</li>
                <li><strong>Credit Account</strong> - Access to 50,000 RWF credit limit</li>
            </ul>

            <p>To activate your account and start using our services, please verify your email address:</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <p><strong>Verification Code: <span class="highlight">{{otp}}</span></strong></p>
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">This code expires in 10 minutes</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Quick Tips:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Maintain good repayment history to improve your credit score</li>
                <li>Higher credit scores unlock better interest rates</li>
                <li>Upgrade your account tier for higher limits</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Need help? Our support team is here for you 24/7.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Credit Jambo Ltd</strong></p>
            <p>Digital Credit & Savings Platform</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
